## üí∞ Xactimate-Style Estimates

### Generate Insurance Estimates

```bash
GET /api/remediation/dryout/1/xactimate-format
GET /api/remediation/reconstruction/1/xactimate-estimate
```

**Output Format:**
```json
{
  "project_number": "RECON-2025-001",
  "claim_number": "SF-123456789",
  "line_items": [
    {
      "code": "DEM-CARPT",
      "category": "Demolition",
      "description": "Remove carpet",
      "qty": 850,
      "unit": "SF",
      "rate": 0.75,
      "total": "637.50"
    },
    {
      "code": "FLR-CRPT",
      "category": "Flooring",
      "description": "Install carpet - Berber, 40oz",
      "qty": 850,
      "unit": "SF",
      "rate": 4.25,
      "total": "3612.50"
    }
  ],
  "summary": {
    "subtotal": "45750.00",
    "overhead": "10% = $4575.00",
    "profit": "10% = $5032.50",
    "total": "55357.50"
  }
}
```

