### Required Photos for Insurance
```javascript
POST /api/remediation/dryout/1/photos
{
  "photo_type": "Before",
  "room_location": "Living Room",
  "description": "Water damage to carpet and drywall - north wall",
  "file_path": "/photos/project-1/before-living-room-001.jpg",
  "taken_by": "Mike Johnson"
}
```

**Photo Types:**
- Before
- During
- After
- Thermal (infrared)
- Moisture meter readings
- Equipment placement
- Demo progress
- Reconstruction progress

